ts/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你話香港人廢 咁點姐 你有無睇呀壽頭<br />\n英格蘭勁你身為香港人有乜柒值得自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地會因為你撐英格蘭好欣賞你？ 佢地心諗條屎忽鬼係咪痴撚左線咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人廢就唔撐係咪勝利球迷黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問心啦 佢兩個傷心你會鄧邊個肉痛呀仆街英奴<br />\n你地堆英奴死撚左去啦 比粒牛丸收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好用唔用用朗尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n柒撚完未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收啦英奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e9ead9d2afdfb500417c5574912229e41b3c00","tid":468763,"uid":25916,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T17:07:54.000Z","msg":"需然沙基利平時好廢 但今次講得幾好"},{"pid":"796fcda2f8082ff5e3acfac54ed399280295bc56","tid":468763,"uid":141957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T17:12:46.000Z","msg":"意粉但今場都有現場睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本無衝突"},{"pid":"21a57f1dbc5107428353932595994ace0f1634b3","tid":468763,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T17:17:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>完場後坐係109到呆撚左 欲哭無淚<br />\n<br />\nbtw請珍惜黃洋⋯⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\nMe坐係103哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都喺103<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\